co.cask.tigon.test
Class SQLFlowTestBase

java.lang.Object
  co.cask.tigon.test.TestBase
      co.cask.tigon.test.SQLFlowTestBase

public class SQLFlowTestBase
extends TestBase

This is a base class that provides all the common functionality to test a Tigon SQL Flow. The contract to be followed is that the last flowlet of the Flow that is being tested, pings output data packets to an http end-point specified in the runtime args as "baseURL".
